374
00:29:07,841 --> 00:29:09,467
- Cepatlah.
- Baik, Tuan.

375
00:29:20,812 --> 00:29:21,896
Siapa itu?

376
00:29:39,747 --> 00:29:40,832
Siapa itu?

377
00:29:47,213 --> 00:29:48,214
Inspektur Ketiga.

378
00:29:49,257 --> 00:29:52,135
Kami mencari seseorang
atas perintah Konselor Kedua.

379
00:29:53,094 --> 00:29:55,305
Ini kediaman sahabatku.

380
00:29:55,930 --> 00:29:59,017
Aku tak tahu kalian cari siapa,
tapi dia tak ada di sini.

381
00:29:59,267 --> 00:30:00,435
Tuan sendirian di sini?

382
00:30:00,518 --> 00:30:02,437
Saat ini aku menunggu sendirian

383
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,980
