384
00:30:06,274 --> 00:30:07,859
Maaf merepotkan.

385
00:30:25,585 --> 00:30:26,836
Jangan khawatir.

386
00:30:28,296 --> 00:30:29,547
Kau sudah aman.

387
00:30:38,223 --> 00:30:39,682
Bagaimana kau bisa menemukanku?

388
00:30:40,266 --> 00:30:42,602
Jawab. Kau membuntutiku selama ini?

389
00:30:42,685 --> 00:30:45,980
Kau mengawasi perbuatanku
selama bertahun-tahun?

390
00:30:46,231 --> 00:30:47,398
Mo-hwa.

391
