layaknya kakakku sendiri.

394
00:31:16,719 --> 00:31:18,596
Jangan muncul lagi seumur hidupku,

395
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:20,431
atau akan kubunuh kau...

396
00:31:23,142 --> 00:31:24,644
tanpa ragu.

397
00:31:33,111 --> 00:31:35,280
Seharusnya ada di daerah sini.

398
00:31:37,323 --> 00:31:39,742
Rumah dengan 33 kamar,

399
00:31:40,326 --> 00:31:42,537
dan pohon pir di halaman depan.

400
00:31:45,498 --> 00:31:47,583
- Aneh, 'kan?
- Maaf?

401
00:31:47,667 --> 00:31:49,627
Aku tak lihat seorang pun dari tadi.

402
00:31:50,211 --> 00:31:51,879
Itu karena sudah larut malam.

403
00:31:52,463 --> 00:31:54,549
